videos.description: Chandler Cox runs in a score to get the Tigers on the board first in the early minutes of the first quarter.
videos.headline: Cox crashes in for 1-yard Auburn TD

videos.description: Auburn's Marlon Davidson blocks a 48-yard Tennessee field goal try in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Davidson blocks Tennessee FG

videos.description: Tennessee's Jarrett Guarantano finds Ty Chandler who runs 42 yards untouched for a Volunteers touchdown.
videos.headline: Guarantano hits Chandler for 42-yard Vols TD

videos.description: Jarrett Stidham finds Anthony Schwartz who flies down the field for an Auburn touchdown in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Schwartz takes off for 76-yard Auburn TD

videos.description: Jarrett Guarantano finds Jauan Jennings in the end zone for a 25-yard Tennessee touchdown to give the Volunteers a 20-17 lead in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Guarantano drops a dime for Tennessee TD
